.SS \fBincoming_extractor.pvrpack\fP
.sp
Reader for the Incoming \fB*_T.PVR\fP Dreamcast texture\-pack container.
.sp
A pack begins with a table of contents made of \fB(absolute offset, size)\fP pairs of unsigned 32\-bit
little\-endian integers, terminated by a zero entry. The byte length of the table equals the offset
of its first entry. Each entry points at a standard Dreamcast PVRT chunk.
